          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_1_p_8"><b>Annex A – Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>66 </num>
              <p>The Act extends to the whole of the United Kingdom with the exception of two consequential amendments which have the same (limited) extent as the enactment being amended.</p>
            </blockContainer>
